#### Files Modified

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [dashboard.py](file:///d:/Content_Engine/ui/dashboard.py) | Added Tab 4 "CSV Ingestor" with upload + column mapping + editable JSON config + fast pipeline call |
| [knowledge_graph.py](file:///d:/Content_Engine/src/knowledge_graph.py) | Added `precomputed_vector` param + `batch_merge_edges()` with UNWIND |
